solated due to data-sharing limitations across multiple parties, a...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.12584", "source": "arXiv CS ML", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.12584v1/2605.12584v1/x1.png", "score": 10}, {"id": "oai:arXiv.org:2605.12620v1", "title": "Think Twice, Act Once: Verifier-Guided Action Selection For Embodied Agents", "summary": "Abstract: Building generalist embodied agents capable of solving complex real-world tasks remains a fundamental challenge in AI. Multimodal Large Language Models (MLLMs) have significantly advanced the reasoning capabilities of such agents through strong vision-language knowledge and chain-of-though...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.12620", "source": "arXiv AI", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.12620v1/2605.12620v1/x1.png", "score": 9}]}